(I)(a)(iii) 污水樣本檢測呈陽性的地點
Places with Sewage Sample(s) Tested Positive
指明任何曾於以下指明期間及時段身處指明地點的人士（不論以何種身分身處該等
地點，包括但不限於全職、兼職和替假員工、住客、學生及訪客，另有指明者除外）
為指明類別人士[見附註]：
Specify any persons who had been present at the following specified places during the
specified date(s) and time period(s) (in any capacity including but not limited to full-time,
part-time and relief staff, residents, students and visitors, unless otherwise specified) as the
specified category of persons[Note]:
